oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Crow family
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Front row, l-r: Millie Martin Crow, Arnold Crow, Louise Martin Crow, Basil Lloyd Crow, Gracie Clifton Crow, Stanley Eugene Crow. Back row, l-r: Alice Ann Few, Louise Roberts Few, Hollie Few Crow, Darden Crow, Larry Crow, Hollie Mae Crow.
All adults pictured were World War II workers, except Louise Few. All lived in the house pictured behind them except Louise & Alice Few.
